    Should Contain X Times    ${output}    action :     1
    Should Contain X Times    ${output}    value :     1
    Should Contain X Times    ${output}    x : 32.4811    1
    Should Contain X Times    ${output}    y : 58.9156    1
    Should Contain X Times    ${output}    z : 6.7142    1
